Indeed you should configure {{yarn.resourcemanager.recovery.enabled}} for the ResourceManager to recover jobs. 

Recovery is documented here: https://hadoop.apache.org/docs/current/hadoop-yarn/hadoop-yarn-site/ResourceManagerRestart.html

